# Tcrt5000
in this project we are going to setup tcrt5000 and use it to detect black and white lines , useful for linefollower robots .
## Components
___________________________________________________
* Tcrt5000
* resistor 10k
* resistor 220
### Image
![tcrt5000](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
## Prerequisites
_________________________________________________
* Arduino IDE
* Arduino Uno
* The component mentioned
## Run locally
______________________________________________
Clone the project 

    git clone https://github.com/sladememarian/Tcrt5000_amirpouyan_MRA1400.git
> 1. Open the code.ino from code directory in Arduino IDE
> 2. Plug in you Arduino Uno 
> 3. Upload the program
